data.description: This American Foursquare Style home is a hidden treasure!  Fall in love with this historic home from the moment you step into the lovely 3 season porch that has been raised and new front door & new dbl pane windows. Step through the double doors and discover the AMAZING hardwood floors and beautiful woodwork all throughout the home!  The Livingroom is adorned with a leaded stained glass picture window, and column bases that separate it from the formal dining room.  The swinging door leads you to a galley kitchen with stainless steel appliances that are less than 4 years old. Head up stairs and discover the beautiful custom designed full bathroom adorned with tiled walls & floor, and new toilet and shower.  Four spacious bedrooms are also on the upstairs level.  The spacious attic is yours to finish!  Truly a must see!  The basement offer laundry plus plenty of space to finish as you choose.  The back porch leads to a detached 2 car garage &  outdoor fire pit.  Being sold "AS IS".
